{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5774e7ed68","title":"毛泽东为转发广东省军管会、湖南省军区关于支左工作报告写的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"236a81f96a","index":0,"year":1967,"month":5,"day":14,"articleId":"5774e7ed68"}],"tags":[{"id":"634a5de908","name":"广东文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"70a1e48626","name":"军队支左","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dce00e6de9","name":"湖南文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"98201d9beb","type":"title","text":"为转发广东省军管会、湖南省军区关于支左工作报告写的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5774e7ed68"},{"id":"85b0b5eb39","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5774e7ed68"},{"id":"c9f0a97f2f","type":"appellation","text":"各大军区，各省军区，各军区分，各人民武装部，各军各师各团，直属各军种、兵种：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5774e7ed68"},{"id":"cf5275c1a7","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）现将广州军区、湖南省军区报告两件发给你们，望参照执行。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5774e7ed68"},{"id":"54536dbcf4","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）凡犯了错误的必须坚决改正。如不改正，越陷越深，到头来还得改正，威信损失就太大了。及早改正，威信只会比前更高。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5774e7ed68"},{"id":"2305a6dce3","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）不要动动摇摇，游移不决。听信老婆孩子从保字号那里带来的错话，信以为真。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5774e7ed68"},{"id":"7d2240006b","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）要受得住工人、农民、学生、战士、干部的批评，加以分析，好的接受，错的解释。解释不通，暂时搁下，将来再说。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5774e7ed68"},{"id":"c22db5b26a","type":"paragraph","text":"（五）要坚决相信绝大多数群众是好的，坏人只是极少数，不过百分之一、二、三。这样一想，就什么都通了。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5774e7ed68"}],"page":{"id":"ef7ed27a95","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5774e7ed68","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}